                "invention-title": [
                    "Carbon neutralization system and method for low-carbon development of manufacturing industry",
                    "一种制造业低碳化发展的碳中和系统及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of carbon neutralization systems, and discloses a carbon neutralization system and method for low-carbon development in the manufacturing industry, and the system comprises a carbon collection box, a reaction kettle, a feeding tank and a control unit; the carbon collecting box is used for storing carbon dioxide generated by industrial operation; the reaction kettle comprises a stirring part and a reaction part, the reaction part is communicated with the stirring part through a vent hole, the stirring part is provided with a stirring paddle, the stirring part is used for mixing carbon dioxide and hydrogen, and the reaction part is used for providing a reaction place for methanation of the carbon dioxide; the feeding tank comprises a hydrogen cavity and an oxygen cavity, and electrodes are arranged in the hydrogen cavity and the oxygen cavity respectively; the carbon collecting box is communicated with the stirring part, and the hydrogen cavity is respectively communicated with the stirring part and the reaction part; the control unit comprises an acquisition module, a processing module, a monitoring module and a control module, and by means of the system and method, the generated carbon emission in the manufacturing industry can be reduced or offset, and the net carbon emission is zero."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及碳中和系统技术领域，公开了一种制造业低碳化发展的碳中和系统及方法，其系统包括：集碳箱、反应釜、供料罐与控制单元；所述集碳箱用于储存工业作业产生的二氧化碳；所述反应釜包括搅拌部与反应部，所述反应部与所述搅拌部通过通气孔连通，所述搅拌部设置有搅拌桨，所述搅拌部用于混合二氧化碳与氢气，所述反应部用于提供二氧化碳甲烷化的反应场所；所述供料罐包括氢腔与氧腔，所述氢腔与所述氧腔的内部分别设置有电极；所述集碳箱与所述搅拌部连通，所述氢腔分别与所述搅拌部与反应部连通；所述控制单元包括：采集模块、处理模块、监测模块与控制模块，本发明通过该系统和方法可实现制造业减少或抵消产生的碳排放量，使净碳排放为零。"
                }
            ]
